sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant Agent as Support Agent
    participant Embed as Azure Embeddings
    participant Store as Local JSON Vector Store
    participant LLM as Azure Chat
    participant DB as MongoDB

    User->>API: POST /api/agent (support)
    API->>Agent: question
    Agent->>Embed: generate query embedding
    Embed-->>Agent: embedding vector
    Agent->>Store: similarity search
    Store-->>Agent: top relevant chunks
    Agent->>LLM: question + retrieved context
    LLM-->>Agent: grounded answer
    Agent->>DB: save chat log
    Agent-->>API: answer + sources
    API-->>User: JSON response
